# Host-local overrides (copy to gitignored paths)

This directory is **gitignored**. Put anything that must differ per Spark box here:

- `local/recipes/` — one-off recipe overrides (symlink or copy into use manually)
- `local/env.sh` — source from shell for box-specific exports
- `local/notes.md` — operator scratch pad

**Do not** put shared GB10 cookbook data here — commit `recipes/`, `data/golden-recipes.yaml`,
`data/model-catalog.yaml`, and `data/model-verification.yaml` via `scripts/sparky-safe-push.sh`.

**Never commit:** `data/inference-profiles.yaml`, `data/inference-benchmarks.yaml` (skip-worktree on sparky).

Safe sync on a live box:

```bash
bash scripts/sparky-safe-pull.sh    # pull without stopping inference
bash scripts/sparky-safe-push.sh -m "your message"   # push shared cookbook only
```

See `.cursor/skills/sparky-safe-sync/SKILL.md` and `docs/runbooks/sparky-live-sync.md`.
